column5: Have been getting out lately at night with a buddy and managed to get into some nice largies.  All caught on Senkos of various colours.  Man it's a blast night fishing and waiting to set the hook when these guys are nibblin on the bait....  Here are a few pics.                Then particiapted in the Lift Bridge Salmon Tourney on Sunday.  Had good numbers but nothing big enough for the $'s.  Still a great time.  Here's one of the salmon.......    A great weekend of fishing...  Sherriff
Some beauty looking Bass there Sheriff.  Nice report.
nice report and some beauty fish,congrats
Those are some really nice bass and at night to boot!!! Nice job!
Nice work Jeff.  Some nice early fall fatties you got there.  Corn Nug
nice job,if u think the senkos fun a night u should try a buzzbait
Nice report, btw that sig is hilarious.
